<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy" lastUpdated="January 1, 2026">
    <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your
        personal information. Replace this placeholder text with your own policy.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
        Describe the types of information you collect from visitors, such as
        contact details submitted through forms or analytics data.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>
        Explain the purposes for which you process personal data, such as
        responding to inquiries or improving your services.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
        Outline the rights visitors have regarding their data and how they can
        contact you to exercise them.
    </p>
</LegalLayout>
